metadata.name: Trip To Heaven #1/17
metadata.description:
I have no need to be tethered to this world  
For I’ve found a new life more meaningful beyond  
Peace and joy I knoweth not existed  
Even in the darkest of times

Kitai sezu ni ai o mitsuketa  
Soshite totemo shiryobukai kakebuton  
Hinode no utsukushī uta no yō ni  
Yūgure no heiwana merodī

Watashi wa ai o mitsuketamashita  
Watashi wa kami o mitsuketa
